import Vue from 'vue'
import './plugins/bootstrap-vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import BootstrapVue from 'bootstrap-vue'
import store from './store'
import Vuex from 'vuex'

Vue.use(Vuex)
Vue.use(BootstrapVue)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  store,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
